  "text": "qRT-PCR was performed as previously reported [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] with some modifications. Snap-frozen livers or cultured hepatocytes were homogenized in Trizol reagent (Invitrogen #15596026). RNA isolated according to the manufacturer's protocol was reverse-transcribed using the Qiagen Quantitect reverse transcriptase kit (Qiagen #205310). cDNA was subjected to quantitative PCR using the SYBR Green master mix reagent (Applied Biosystems #4309155). Primer sequences used are available upon request.",
